metadata.name: Lust
metadata.description:
An illegal passion can make you a naive boy running after evil as fast as he can. Or make you a king bowing his head to sin.

Take off the aggressive mask and you will see the helplessness in front of this vice.

Like thorns behind perfect flowers, itâ€™s hidden inside you.

A sensual attraction that shivers through your whole body and hits your head with a thousand-ton sledgehammer.

It's everywhere, there's no escaping it.

You always have a chance to resist vice, but will you stretch out your hand to your savior?
